import React from "react";
import { Card, Button, Container } from "react-bootstrap";

const ProjectDashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Card>
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>
            PROJECTS
            <Button variant="success" className="float-end" id="addProject">
              + Add Project
            </Button>
            <Button variant="light" className="float-end" id="searchProject">
              Search
            </Button>
            <Button
              variant="danger"
              disabled
              className="float-end"
              id="deleteProject"
            >
              Deleted
            </Button>
          </Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>
            With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional
            content.
          </Card.Text>
          <Button variant="primary">Go somewhere</Button>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ProjectDashboard;
